Jones S, Thornton JM, Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. 93, 13-20 (1996)
Ungermannova, D. et al., J. Biomol. Screen. 18, 910–920 (2013)
Past attempts to inhibit Cks1–Skp2 interaction with small molecules yielded unsatisfying results.
Protein–protein interactions are challenging to target using small molecules due to large and flat interfaces.
